descriptionHtml:
== What this mod does? ==
Are you tired of always the same 3D models on Loadscreens!?
This mod adds 40 new 3D loadscreens using models and cameras not used on the regular ones but already there.

== Compatibility ==
It is compatible with all mods, all version on Skyrims with or without Dawnguard.

== Videos ==
